  <revision rev="10" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>61f175259511caf6f8bb33ef199a3ad0</srcmd5>
    <version>1.3.0+git20260618.66fbd03</version>
    <time>1781811452</time>
    <user>anag_factory</user>
    <comment>- Update to version 1.3.0+git20260618.66fbd03:
  * Release version 1.3.0
  * meson.build: try to autodetect distribution variable if not set
  * CI: add tests/ci, a nspawn container based test suite
  * INSTALL.md: document -Ddistribution=suse
  * chfn/chsh: fix return 0 in error case
  * passwd: fix -s in getopt()
  * pwupdd-chfn: move get peer_uid call to later when we need it
  * pwupdd: call getpwnam after unpacking p.name
  * Release version 1.2.1
  * Use strlcpy instead of strcpy
  * Fix several errors</comment>
    <requestid>1360277</requestid>
  </revision>
  <revision rev="11" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>529dbb08ac7b97e0560a779993067a09</srcmd5>
    <version>1.4.0+git20260717.3914e08</version>
    <time>1784306999</time>
    <user>dimstar_suse</user>
    <comment>- Update to version 1.4.0+git20260717.3914e08:
  * Release version 1.4.0
  * CI: add tests for newuidmap/newgidmap/newidmapd
  * newidmapd: fix usage of uid for gid mapping, add more debug output
  * newxidmap/newidmapd: fix strto*l error checks
  * Add newgidmap, newidmapd and newuidmap manual pages
  * newidmapd: use long long to avoid variable overflows
  * Add function is_uid() to check if a token is a UID
  * CI: check that chage help does not contain mindays option
  * CI: print failed test suites
  * TODO: add more things to the list
  * pam_unix_ng/pwaccessd: make expire check configurable (use_sp_min)
  * Add pwaccessd.conf.5 manual page
  * tst-read_config: adjust for new struct config_t
  * chage: deprecate sp_min
  * passwd: deprecate sp_min
  * read_config: add support for SpMin key
  * read_config: make name of configuration file configureable</comment>
    <requestid>1366398</requestid>
  </revision>
